                <p>
                    tiripuvaṉa-c-cakkara-vattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>-cuntara-pāṇṭiya-tēvaṟku yāṇṭu <g type="numeral">10</g> Āvatu kēyya-māṇikka-vaḷaṉāṭṭu vaṭakāl
                    <lb n="2"/>parivaṭṭa nakaram pukalōkattu Uṭaiyār pañcavaṉ mā<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>vi<hi rend="grantha">śu</hi>varam-uṭaiyār kōyilukku tiru-vātavū<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>-nāyaṉārai Ēṟi-Aruḷa paṇṇiṉa ṉākai-y-āṉa
                    <lb n="3"/>cōḻa-ku<supplied reason="omitted">lava</supplied>lli-paṭṭiṉattu tiru-p-paḷḷi-p-pāṟṟu ṉāyakattāril Āṇṭāṉ kōtayāṉa kulōttuṅka-rāyaṉēṉ Iṉ-ṉāyaṉāṟkku Amutupaṭikkum t<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>i</corr></choice>ruviḷakku
                    <lb n="4" break="no"/>m nāyanāṟ<choice><sic>t</sic><corr>k</corr></choice>ku koṇṭa<unclear>ṭa</unclear>kantaṉ uṭaiyān nilamum nattamum Āvatu Ivūr piṭākai cankuṇaveḷi paṇappāṟṟukku vaṭakku taṭi mūṉṟu viṭṭuma
                    <lb n="5" break="no"/>ṟkku Amutupaṭikkum tiruvi
                    <lb n="6"/>Ōṭai Eṉṟu pēr kūvappaṭṭa nilam mā mummāvaraiyum kaṇapati vāykkālukku mēṟkku puṟaṅkarampa-ṉāṭṭu vēḷāṉ maṉaikku valivala-nāṭu vēḷāṉ maṉai Iru
                    <lb n="7" break="no"/>ppukkum 1/10 <g ref="sym:tam-nilam"/> m I-nilamā mummāvaraiyum Iṉ-nāyanāṟku Amutupaṭikkum tiruviḷakkum <hi rend="grantha">can<choice><orig>t</orig><reg>d</reg></choice>rāditya</hi>varai cella-k kaṭavat’ āka-k koṇṭu Iṭṭēṉ Āṇṭāṉ kō
                    <lb n="8"/>taiyāṉa kulōttuṅka-rāyaṉ-ēṉ Ik-kōyil Akrāṇam tiruvārūr ammāṉ Eḻuttu <g ref="sym:dashPlain" type="punctuation">.</g> Ik-kōyil tēvakammi piram<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>ī</reg></choice><hi rend="grantha">śvara</hi>-paṭṭaṉ Eḻuttu
                    <lb n="9"/>Ik-kōyil kaṇakkaṉ paṉaṅk’ uṭaiyāṉ vītiviṭaṅka-p perumāṉ Eḻu<supplied reason="omitted">ttu</supplied>
                    
